{
  "texts": [
    "Many current studies merely conduct standard data preparation and omit the features of different types of text.",
    "To prevent \"garbage-in-garbage-out\", future research can look more deeply into the characteristics of specific texts and prepare the data in a way that fits the characteristics of the texts.",
    "Data selection After text preprocessing, the text data should be further selected or weighted by considering the text features.",
    "This procedure is yet neglected by a substantial number of papers.",
    "For example, Twitter offers millions of short texts daily, but misinformation is omnipresent."
  ]
}